        "A vibrant Mediterranean seafront stretching through one of the Middle East's most dynamic cities.",
        "Tel Aviv's 14-kilometre promenade links golden sandy beaches, outdoor gyms, and buzzing café terraces facing the shimmering Mediterranean. It embodies the city's famously energetic, hedonistic character.\n\nThe adjacent Bauhaus-rich White City offers a UNESCO-listed architectural contrast just steps from the sand. Sunsets here, watched from a beachside bar, are reliably spectacular.",
